1.01 C TEST C1 NEGATIVE ARRAY SUBSCRIPT
1.02 C FOCAL ALLOWS SUBSCRIPTS -2048 TO 2047
1.03 C BUT THE C ARRAY INDEX IS NOT OFFSET SO NEGATIVES UNDERFLOW
1.04 C EXPECTED OUTPUT IS 42 AND 99
1.05 C BUG CAUSES HEAP CORRUPTION MAY SEGFAULT
1.10 SET A(-1)=42
1.20 TYPE "A(-1)  = ",A(-1),!
1.30 SET A(-2048)=99
1.40 TYPE "A(-2048)= ",A(-2048),!
1.50 TYPE !,"TEST COMPLETE",!
1.60 QUIT
